{"tid":1431370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能搞個「受害者遊行」？","createTime":"2019-08-08T03:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:23:04.000Z","uid":6988,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e9acb1218ecd878f5d4570827063e58cfc386811","tid":1431370,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"巴黎數千人參與「受傷者示威」，呼籲禁止使用武器。受傷的示威者在隊伍中打頭陣，其中有些人在眼部貼上表示目標的准心標誌。在上周的示威者單眼失明的示威者傑羅姆&middot;羅德里格斯（Jerome Rodrigues）受到人群鼓掌的熱烈歡迎<br />\n<br />\n將被捕同受傷嘅手足變成重點<br />\n第一可以令咁多位手足知道佢係我地嘅英雄 有好多人support緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其次亦都可以make到noise<br />\n民意亦都可以令大眾明白班狗嘅武力係幾咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad09b8221890df9d8cd047b166384ff11534e2f","tid":1431370,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be40742fffeda209734de252787824dc4719f7c9","tid":1431370,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"俾人拉9晒咪仆街"},{"pid":"a2b53f0e48de86578beeda424da424890c64eaa5","tid":1431370,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=aab03643&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz5gCHn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz5gCHn.png&h=0116ff23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHFPXHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHFPXHp.jpg&h=9c667c5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af89af75cd29e9853ffe593c3d3f3ebaa50a07b5","tid":1431370,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be40742fffeda209734de252787824dc4719f7c9",